r-base (4.3.1-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * debian/rules: Omit debug info on 32-bit OSs to avoid memory limits
    affecting eg rstan (thanks to Adrian Bunk) 		(Closes: #1037439)

  * debian/control: Use libcurses-dev in Depends: of r-base-dev as in
    Build-Depends: of package				(Closes: #1040037)

  * debian/control: Add 'r-graphics-engine-${graphics_engine:Version}'
    to the Provides: for r-base-core
  * debian/rules: Compute graphics engine version based on GraphicsEngine.h
  * debian/r-cran.mk: Extract graphics engine version from Provides:
  							(Closes: #1040038)

  * debian/control: Remove no-longer-needed libpcre3-dev entry in
    Build-Depends and in Depends: of r-base-dev 	(Closes: #1040341)

  * debian/control: Remove Provides: and Conflicts: for 'r-gnome (<=
    2.3.1), r-cran-rcompgen (<= 0.1-17-1)' added in 2006

  * debian/control: Remove Replaces:, Provides:, Conflicts: for
    'r-base-latex' added in 2009

 -- Dirk Eddelbuettel <edd@debian.org>  Wed, 05 Jul 2023 06:36:26 -0500

